Muffin Top offend you?

00:54.075 --> 00:56.004
- No.
- Hmm?

00:56.005 --> 00:57.038
What's your name?

00:57.039 --> 00:59.012
- Rachel.
- Little Miss...

00:59.015 --> 01:01.088
- David Schwimmer?
- Little Miss David Schwimmer.

01:01.091 --> 01:05.019
I bet you were
a big star back in Iowa.

01:05.021 --> 01:07.012
- I'm actually from Ohio.
- Ohio.

01:07.013 --> 01:08.046
That's even worse.

01:08.047 --> 01:10.028
You ever look at a map?

01:10.029 --> 01:13.479
Ohio is like a giant turd that
Michigan just can't pinch off.

01:13.480 --> 01:15.811
So did you come all the way
to New York City

01:15.812 --> 01:17.071
to show me how to run my class?

01:17.072 --> 01:20.058
