01:34.046 --> 01:36.024
Higher. Higher.

01:36.025 --> 01:38.020
Into the ground.
Higher!

01:38.021 --> 01:39.083
Higher, higher!

01:39.084 --> 01:42.046
- Come on!
- I don't need any help.

01:42.047 --> 01:44.217
No, no, sweetie, I'm not
coming down here to help you.

01:44.218 --> 01:47.016
